# Loan Approval Classifier

This project builds a Machine Learning model that predicts whether a loan should be approved or rejected based on applicant information.

## Technologies Used
- Python
- Pandas
- Scikit-learn
- Logistic Regression

## Features
- Data preprocessing
- Train/Test split
- Feature scaling
- Logistic Regression model
- Model evaluation (Accuracy, Confusion Matrix)

## How to Run

1. Install dependencies

pip install -r requirements.txt

2. Run the model

python Loan approval calssifier.py